    "topic": "Practice Example 2",
    "subtopics": [
      {
        "subtopic": "Upstream Time",
        "content": "**Q:** Speed of boat = 15 km/hr, speed of stream = 3 km/hr. How much time to go 36 km upstream?\n**Solution:**\nUpstream speed = 15 − 3 = 12 km/hr\nTime = 36/12 = 3 hours\n**Answer:** 3 hours"
      }
